        "QuestionText_Unsafe": "<p><strong>[WARM-UP PLACEHOLDER]</strong></p><p><em>(Warm-up rating — add manually after import using Qualtrics Conjoint module, 1 profile, with timer JS attached.)</em></p><p>Attach <code>javascript/timer-high-pressure.js</code> to the warm-up Conjoint question (high-pressure branch only) and set embedded data <code>warmup_discarded = true</code> on submit.</p>"
